&lt;p>주요 개념과 기능&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>JSX (JavaScript XML)
JSX는 JavaScript 안에서 HTML과 유사한 문법을 사용할 수 있게 해주는 문법적 확장입니다:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-jsx" data-lang="jsx">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">function&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">ProductCard&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">({&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">})&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">className&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;product-card&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">src&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">alt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">/&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">description&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">button&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">onClick&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">alert&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sb">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">${&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">product&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">price&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sb">원`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)}&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">가격&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">보기&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">button&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
